movie.title: The Magic School Bus Rides Again: The Frizz Connection
movie.title_english: The Magic School Bus Rides Again: The Frizz Connection
movie.title_long: The Magic School Bus Rides Again: The Frizz Connection (2020)
movie.description_intro: A lightning separates the Magic School Bus into three pieces, scattering the class across the globe with different versions of Ms. Frizzle aboard each bus.

movies.title: The Incredible Hulk
movies.summary: Depicting the events after the Gamma Bomb. 'The Incredible Hulk' tells the story of Dr Bruce Banner, who seeks a cure to his unique condition, which causes him to turn into a giant green monster under emotional stress. Whilst on the run from military which seeks his capture, Banner comes close to a cure. But all is lost when a new creature emerges: The Abomination.

movies.title: Cyber Bride
movies.summary: After his wife tragically dies, a desperate widowed husband finds a service online that can bring her back - But not all is as it seems.

movies.title: Geo-Disaster
movies.summary: A family in Los Angeles finds themselves separated during a convergence of history's greatest disasters: a super volcano, a mega earthquake and a massive twister. While the world endures this near apocalyptic event, our heroes must persevere on their own skills and wit to reunite and survive.
